data.description: Large corner lot with a home that is Cute! Quaint! And close to everything Oakland. This is the perfect starter home. Minutes commute via 580 to Downtown Oakland, SF, Berkeley.  Backyard is perfect for outdoor wine, dine, Friday unwind sessions among the trees and beautiful bougainvillea type foliage. Here's your chance to own in Oakland! Turn detached garage into to an ADU or Studio.
